item.dc:creator: @dragonman2 dragonman2
item.description:
@dragonman2 wrote:

[quote=“Moparisthebest, post:38, topic:346052”][quote author=dragonman2 link=topic=442431.msg3249243#msg3249243 date=1277611120]
Moparscapeisthebest:

And my server isnt offline. im on it right now. its hosted from a vps. and its still not on list…

[/quote]

I tested your server manually, right now it is online and accessible to my server. So next time the servers are updated (about every 30 minutes) it should be added to the online list automatically, assuming that it is still online then.

Also, a VPS doesn’t mean it will be online all the time. Most servers still use ‘autorestarters’ which make them offline every so often, and also sometimes there is too much traffic or a bad route in the middle of our servers and my server won’t be able to connect to yours in the alloted amount of time, which tells my server it’s offline. It’s the internet, deal with it. :)[/quote]
